%% Data Flow Diagram for ilab-on-ocp
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-2.19/ilab-on-ocp.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant DSPA as Data Science Pipelines<br/>(DSPA)
    participant PreReq as prerequisites_check<br/>Pod
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant SDGPod as sdg_op<br/>Pod
    participant Git as Git Repository<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Teacher as Teacher Model (Mixtral)<br/>KServe Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TrainPod as training<br/>Pod
    participant PTJob as PyTorchJob<br/>Master + Workers
    participant EvalMT as mt_bench<br/>Pod
    participant EvalFinal as final_eval<br/>Pod
    participant Judge as Judge Model (Prometheus)<br/>KServe Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant vLLM as localhost vLLM<br/>dynamic/TCP HTTP
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MR as Model Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over DSPA: Pipeline triggered via DSPA<br/>(managedPipelines.instructLab.state: Managed)

    DSPA->>PreReq: Launch prerequisites_check
    PreReq->>K8sAPI: GET secrets, LIST CRDs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>PreReq: Validated
    PreReq->>Teacher: POST /chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Teacher-->>PreReq: OK
    PreReq->>Judge: POST /chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Judge-->>PreReq: OK

    DSPA->>SDGPod: Launch sdg_op
    SDGPod->>Git: Clone taxonomy<br/>Auth: PAT or SSH Key<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Git-->>SDGPod: Taxonomy data
    SDGPod->>Teacher: POST /chat/completions (batch)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Teacher-->>SDGPod: Synthetic training data
    Note over SDGPod: Write synthetic data to PVC<br/>(ReadWriteMany)

    DSPA->>TrainPod: Launch training
    TrainPod->>K8sAPI: CREATE PyTorchJob<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>TrainPod: PyTorchJob created
    Note over PTJob: Phase 1: Knowledge Training<br/>Phase 2: Skills Training<br/>Multi-node multi-GPU
    PTJob->>PTJob: torchrun NCCL<br/>MASTER_PORT/TCP<br/>plaintext (cluster-internal)
    PTJob-->>TrainPod: Training complete
    Note over TrainPod: Trained model on PVC

    DSPA->>EvalMT: Launch mt_bench
    EvalMT->>vLLM: Start local vLLM server<br/>Load candidate model
    EvalMT->>vLLM: POST /v1/models<br/>HTTP plaintext (localhost)
    vLLM-->>EvalMT: Model ready
    EvalMT->>Judge: POST /chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Judge-->>EvalMT: MT-Bench scores

    DSPA->>EvalFinal: Launch final_eval
    EvalFinal->>vLLM: POST /v1 (MMLU eval)<br/>HTTP plaintext (localhost)
    vLLM-->>EvalFinal: MMLU results
    EvalFinal->>Judge: POST /chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Judge-->>EvalFinal: Final evaluation scores

    DSPA->>SDGPod: Launch upload_model
    Note over SDGPod: (runs in utils component)
    SDGPod->>OCI: Push ModelCar image (skopeo)<br/>Auth: dockerconfigjson<br/>TLS 1.2+
    OCI-->>SDGPod: Push complete
    SDGPod->>MR: POST model registration<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    MR-->>SDGPod: Model registered
